Notes:
1. This procfs project is used to note that how to access /proc file with
   standard filesystem method (file operations)-
2. Structure proc_dir_entry has been modified from kernel 3.10, so the read_
   proc function and write_proc should be modified as fops->read and fops->
   write.

Release History:
/******************************************************************************
 * Release Information
 * Project: procfs
 * Version: V0.2
 * Date	  : 2014/1/2
 ******************************************************************************/
 1. Access /proc file with standard filesystem (fops, read)-
 2. Add standard filesystem write function into procfs.c (fops, write)-

/******************************************************************************
 * Release Information
 * Project: procfs
 * Version: V0.1
 * Date	  : 2013/12/23
 ******************************************************************************/ 1. Access /proc file with standard filesystem (fops, read)-
